############################
# Assets – selective ignore
############################

/Server 

# 1) Scripts: keep Scripts, but ignore Utils subfolder
/Assets/Scripts/Utils/

# 2) Do NOT include sample / template / test assets
/Assets/Samples/
/Assets/Resources/
/Assets/Materials/
/Assets/CompositionLayers/
/Assets/_Recovery/
/Assets/MRTemplateAssets/
/Assets/Settings/
/Assets/Test/
/Assets/TextMeshPro/
/Assets/TransclucentImageAsset/
/Assets/XR/
/Assets/XRI/

# 3) Scenes: keep Scenes, but ignore some subfolders
/Assets/Scenes/Legacy/
/Assets/Scenes/SampleScene/

# 4) Plugins: we DO keep
# (No ignore rule here → Assets/Plugins 전체 커밋됨)
# 필요하다면, 명시적으로 manifest 포함시키고 싶으면 아래처럼 적어도 됨:
!/Assets/Plugins/Android/AndroidManifest.xml

